post_text:
Attn Lions Sports Fans! We have great news to share about another Facebook Live broadcast.

You can watch NR Sports LIVE on Sept. 2 to see NRHS Girls Soccer. The game will be broadcast on the new NR Media page;
https://www.facebook.com/events/398173277820920

This picture from AD Doug Foote says it all! Our NRHS freshman boys basketball team just wrapped up a great regular season with a punctuation mark. They took the championship at the Western Brown tournament.

Overall, the NRHS boys basketball program had a memorable season. AD Foote shared these stats:

The Freshman Team was 18-4 winning the WB tournament;

JV was 16-5;

Varsity was 17-5 winning the SBAAC American Division!

Thanks for the great season NRHS basketball!

